Installation Instruction
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

You can watch guide on youtube 

In video i am using Bluestack on PC, but backups was tested and created on phone.
Tested on:

- Samsung Galaxy Note II N7100
- Samsung I9000 Galaxy S
- Xiaomi Mi3W
- Bluestack

Step 1: unpack rar archive	
        Password for rar archive is Slovenia2014

Step 2: Copy to sdcard

Step 3: instal Titanium Backup and when prompted grant root acces

Step 4: Then on sdcard click on game backup something.TiBkp	
        Titanium backup starts importing backup

Step 5: Click on app+Data for full content(all unlocked, a lot of money...)

Step 6: Enjoy!!! :)
